== com_Calendar

Calendar provides a simple calendar for Joomla! 1.5 websites. It allows:

* creation of multiple calendars
* month view of calendar
* adding events to specific dates
* view an upcoming events list
* ajaxified popovers of events

== Roadmap

Future versions are planned to include:

* ajax calendar for moving between months
* color coding events
* color coding calendars
* iCal publishing of calendars